metadata.title: WOCE  P14N - July/ August  1993  CTD and Bottle  Data Report

creators.name: Gunnar  I. Roden, University of Washington (UW), School of Oceanography

metadata.description: High resolution, top to bottom observations in the central Aleutians  (Baron's of Standard) by deoprophic (T,S,O) and hydrochemical (O2, PO4, NO3, SiO4)  categories. Line goes from  59째 N 174째 W to 50째 N 179째 E and then to Fiji.  18 stations are inside the Bering Sea.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: Part of the World Ocean Circulation Experiment (WOCE) to observe (top to bottom) in Aleutians  (Baron's of Standard) by deoprophic (T,S,O) and hydrochemical (O2, PO4, NO3, SiO4) categories.
